25|$|As of 2009, Iran has no <b>capital</b> <b>gains</b> <b>tax</b> on {{the sale}} of real estate assets. However, <b>a</b> <b>capital</b> <b>gain</b> <b>tax</b> will be {{introduced}} with the implementation of the 2010 economic reform plan.|$|R
