5000|$|Every {{individual}} has <b>an</b> annual <b>capital</b> <b>gains</b> <b>tax</b> allowance: <b>gains</b> below the allowance {{are exempt from}} tax, and capital losses can be set against <b>capital</b> <b>gains</b> in other holdings before taxation. All individuals are exempt from tax up to a specified amount of <b>capital</b> <b>gains</b> per year. For the 2015/16 tax year this [...] "annual exemption" [...] is £11,100.|$|R
